It is important to note that the official portraits for [Gerald Ford](/Gerald_Ford), [Jimmy Carter](/Jimmy_Carter), [Ronald Reagan](/Ronald_Reagan), [George H. W. Bush](/George_H._W._Bush), [Bill Clinton](/Bill_Clinton), [George W. Bush](/George_W._Bush), and [Barack Obama](/Barack_Obama) were created by artists who were not employed by the federal government at the time of their commissions. Consequently, these images are not considered to be in the [public domain](/Public_domain) and are therefore not included in this specific gallery. A complete compilation of these portraits can be found via the White House Historical Association's listing. The portraits of [Donald Trump](/Donald_Trump) and [Joe Biden](/Joe_Biden) by the White House Historical Association are still awaiting their official unveiling.

